snippet.title: PlayStation - Wedding Peach - Doki Doki Oironaoshi (1996) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Wedding Peach: Doki Doki Oironaoshi is a Strategy game, developed and published by KSS, which was released in Japan in 1996.
